# Dataset: silver_restaurants

## Silver Layer Purpose
Standardized restaurant master dataset used for restaurant intelligence and regional analytics.

---

## Cleaning Rules

| Column | Cleaning Logic |
|---|---|
| Restaurant | Remove duplicate names |
| City | Standardize city names |
| Food type | Standardize cuisine categories |
| Avg ratings | Validate rating range |
| Delivery time | Validate delivery duration |

---

## Validation Framework

| Validation Category | Rule |
|---|---|
| Rating Validation | Ratings between 1–5 |
| City Validation | Valid city names only |
| Delivery Validation | Delivery time > 0 |
| Duplicate Validation | Restaurant IDs unique |

---

